Package jdkc_exchange

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdkc_exchange.Group
  • public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which implements the concept of Group. A Group object contains memberships, members, questions, and answers. A Group is identified by its title, which is unique among Groups. A Group is also identified by its description which does not have to be unique. The Group object acts as a container for related Questions and the Answers that members add to them.
    See Also:
    Membership
